SUMMARY:The Gothard Sisters at The Old Church Concert Hall
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the coming of Spring with internationally acclaimed Celtic folk group The Gothard Sisters. The three sisters present a high-energy\, festive evening weaving together Celtic fiddle tunes\, Irish songs and ballads\, Irish step dancing and more. Great for the whole family – a perfect annual tradition! \nThis event is over $30. We only include links for higher-priced events from our advertisers — but it’s easy to find with a quick search!
