SUMMARY:Pro-Justice Parenting Discussion
DESCRIPTION:Come build your queer family community with other LGBTQIA+ families for our monthly Queer Kin Collective gathering\, this time hosted at the amazing Second Shapes Bookstore in Kenton! Parents-to-be also very welcome\, as are kids of all ages (though we seem to veer quite young 🙂 ) \nAlways free\, with donations appreciated as we are a volunteer-run collective. Snacks and bevs for all ages provided\, plus some connection prompts for parents and activities for the littles. \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
