DESCRIPTION:Enjoy the outdoors and volunteer as a family — help us clean up camp! \n\n\nClean cabins for summer \n\n\nClean bath house \n\n\nClean outdoor food prep area \n\n\nBring a sack lunch\, water bottle and rubber gloves. \nDress for the weather! \nYouth 15 and under must be accompanied by an adult. \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission. \n 
