SUMMARY:Let's Celebrate Water Safety!
DESCRIPTION:Spring into water safety! Join us March 14 for family-friendly tips\, life jacket try-ons & fun with Goldfish Swim School.\n\n\n\n🌊 Spring Into Water Safety! 🌞\nFree Family Event at Little Nestlings\nSaturday\, March 14 | 10:00–11:00 AM \nSpring break is around the corner\, and summer will be here before we know it! Whether you’re heading to the pool\, the beach\, the river\, or planning backyard splash time\, now is the perfect moment to brush up on water safety skills. \nJoin us at Little Nestlings for a special Water Safety event featuring our friends from Goldfish Swim School – West Linn. This engaging\, family-friendly hour will help your child build confidence around water while giving grown-ups practical tips for keeping everyone safe. \nWhat to Expect:\n\nHands-on water safety lessons for children and caregivers\nTry-on time with real life jackets so kids can practice and feel confident\nPractical tips for pool\, beach\, and river safety\nFun giveaways\nInteractive learning (yes\, it will be fun!)\n\nWater safety isn’t just a summer conversation — it’s a year-round skill that saves lives. Starting these conversations before spring break and summer swim season helps children feel prepared\, not scared. \nPlease RSVP so we can plan accordingly and have enough materials for everyone. \nLet’s head into spring and summer feeling confident\, prepared\, and ready for safe water fun! 🌊 \n Editor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/lets-celebrate-water-safety/
LOCATION:Little Nestlings Early Learning Center\, 19200 Willamette Drive\, West Linn\, O\, 97068\, United States
CATEGORIES:Kids Calendar
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/goldfish-safety-clinic-3.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Little Nestlings Early Learning Center":MAILTO:colleen.littlenestlings@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
