SUMMARY:Kids' Mornings at Oaks Park Roller Rink
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy a kid-centered skating session featuring a special playlist of kid-friendly hits\, skate games\, a visit from Chipper the Squirrel. \nDuring October-May\, the session also features a short group lesson taught by a certified coach. \nOne adult skates free per child. \nSaturdays\, 10-11:30 AM\n$13 per child\n10 & younger only
